{"type": "article", "id": 49589, "title": "可以写字的手腕硅胶带，一种新型备忘录 ｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-01-25T22:44:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 47308, "name": "Lambert & Fils"}, {"id": 47309, "name": "Relaxing"}, {"id": 47310, "name": "Kenma"}, {"id": 47311, "name": "Zeitraum"}, {"id": 47312, "name": "Danao Living"}, {"id": 47313, "name": "Nova Obiecta"}, {"id": 22532, "name": "Patricia Urquiola"}, {"id": 47314, "name": "Agape"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 140, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180125101144vEtzcdAaZ5C78INm.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 14.0px; font: 12.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #2131a1; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 14.0px; font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #2131a1; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 14.0px; font: 12.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333; background-color: #ffffff} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 14.0px; font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 12.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Outdoor Cuff Collection by Ann Marie Vering for Danao Living</h3><p>总部设在美国的 Danao Living 是一家巴厘岛风格的户外家具制造商，最近与洛杉矶设计师 Ann Marie Vering 合作设计了 Cuff 系列新品，八件桌椅新品，都像是戴上了弯曲流线的手镯一般。</p><p>整个系列弯曲的框架采用不锈钢材质制成，半透明的定制编织方式允许光线和空气的流通，在阳光下复杂斑驳的剪影落在地面上，给人带来一种视觉上的轻盈感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101216lEP8DIYZ1KhzdwBp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.614062\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101217WxStyo3cOnB85ACE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.729688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101217qdJsnjWBSR4cTG3M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.468750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801251012176z2O9a8iRV4YNDIl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.452344\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101217KqPeHFTyAi40L9WI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639062\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101217HqB624wiCQoche87.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.483594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101217XLc8N0y5kw7mOWD2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.517188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Danao Living</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Floating YOMA Bed by kaschkasch for Zeitraum</h3><p>这是德国极简实木家具品牌 Zeitraum 与设计师 kaschkasch 的第二次合作。Floating YOMA 是一款看上去似是漂浮在地板上的双人床，据称设计师的灵感源自于蒲团，时下流行的沙发床的流线造型被设计师融入其中。它让人联想到日式榻榻米，但设计师意在创造一个更现代的欧洲版本，更加舒适和简约。</p><p>低矮的框架创造浮动感，四周延伸出来的边缘可以当作书架或是边桌使用。如果你想靠着床坐，滑动的靠背满足舒适性，也可以根据需求移动。圆润的床角确保用户不慎碰到时不会伤到自己。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101402rZXib3tKAT5eDcs6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101401QmL4TJs56BbC1OGU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801251014022vYhwbSRXa4y6qGd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101402vTp2HEonPZjk94SK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801251014021mEt7z5FJZainsMX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018012510140296kFQybBGwxhCruI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lariana Bathroom Line by Patricia Urquiola for Agape</h3><p>西班牙当红设计师 Patricia Urquiola 最近又扩大了自己的设计版图，与意大利顶级卫浴品牌 Agape 合作，带来了 Lariana 系列新品，意在向意大利最受欢迎的旅行目的地之一科莫湖致敬，最近她刚刚完成了那里的五星级酒店 Il Sereno 的设计。</p><p>Lariana 系列包括一款线条简洁的浴缸，轮廓紧凑，意在贴合 20 世纪初的米兰建筑风格。此外还包括两个洗手盆，分为椭圆形和圆形。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101433YhCmo7M6JxfrPi5E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749219\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101433wO8BCqbSlHjEAhpo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.981250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801251014330hDrdXIxmqU7Atiy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.981250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801251014333wXIVpLSNnvCoPJM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.226563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101433RBy6ak95ZxYbdzAT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.621094\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101433MLilXqs9VjzGQeEk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>wemo: Wearable Memos by Kenma </h3><p>你可能也遇到过这样的状况，从杂货店或是超市采购归来，才意识到忘了买一个很重要的东西。或者还有其他的情况，比如工作中必须立即记住某个关键细节。</p><p>日本设计公司 Kenma 打算解决这些问题，他们设计了一款可穿戴的硅胶备忘录，可以系在手腕上，据称其灵感源自护士工作时常在手上记录的习惯。</p><p>设计师认为，不只是医疗领域，包括制造业、建筑业、法律行业、灾害现场的工作人员，甚至是老年人或是阿尔兹海默病患者等，都可能需要这样的东西。记录在腕带上的内容可以用手指或橡皮轻轻擦掉。值得一提的是，即便腕带被弄湿，记录内容也不会受到影响，便于用户洗手或是在水下工作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101502jtvo2m9ibXuQMDT5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801251015022DLp8evZVb5xSwiO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101502mTkLNzp27na3h8KH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101503Sr30RYGZKzNvwgAh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101503xqQA0zMZLmCUXVpo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018012510150371qBGCfW9mA4QROv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>A Sculptural Chair for Relaxing by Nova Obiecta</h3><p>总部位于法国的设计团队的 Nova Obiecta 进军家具设计行业已有五年时间，他们的新作是为品牌 Relaxing 设计的雕塑椅 PARA（D）。</p><p>设计师希望赋予 PARA（D）的俏皮样式，可以邀请用户坐下来，沉浸在他们的幻想中，柔和的色调和圆润的线条，都意在让人们放松下来，夏日游泳池里散发出的假日气息。椅子的轮廓模仿了游泳池梯子的曲线，由漆面钢管和可洗织物制成，适用于室内和室外。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101527WvwUAkfxs6G3VcBh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101527fZkHunEaNVTqW7C0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101527lExV3On7aiweI8Mg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101527XF3oDYjwIRrxGvPJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801251015276oQX94Ej05YfZbuC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mile Collection by Lambert &amp; Fils</h3><p>Mile 系列吊灯是蒙特利尔公司 Lambert &amp; Fils 和设计师 Guillaume Sasseville 的合作，两个直线轮廓的吊灯组合成十字形式，一个朝上，一个朝下，像是办公场景中常见的带状吊灯，又融入了创新的灯光用法，上下散射出去的光芒丰富了空间光线的层次感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101632pCB5rIVHzj7qwut9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101548dukgJqDPHAm3UwMO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101548nsXLI2qdNC4eMG61.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180125101548rA31MHFCVveu2oQb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801251015497w0iC1mUsGYjoflp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}